1
00:00:18,590 --> 00:00:20,660
Wh-Why are you doing this?

2
00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:22,230
"Why," you ask?

3
00:00:23,220 --> 00:00:27,960
Because it's dim here, and there are no people here.

4
00:00:29,630 --> 00:00:32,650
And because it is a good place to sleep.

5
00:00:37,440 --> 00:00:39,780
How does the next part go?

6
00:00:42,810 --> 00:00:44,850
You insolent fool!

7
00:00:48,250 --> 00:00:51,140
Oh, he's pretty good!

8
00:01:02,210 --> 00:01:06,210
If it is your law to kill a Cheonin, who snuck into the capital city,
(Cheonin is the lowest class in Silla society)

9
00:01:06,210 --> 00:01:09,390
my rule is to kill the nobleman who crosses this line.

10
00:01:12,270 --> 00:01:15,920
If you want to beat me up, cross the line first. I'll let you be my opponent.

11
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:17,430
Episode 2

12
00:01:17,430 --> 00:01:21,680
Does it make sense that you want to sleep with that kind of atmosphere out there?

13
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:25,100
I don't think you understand.

14
00:01:25,100 --> 00:01:28,870
It's impossible to put someone to sleep with my stories.

15
00:01:28,870 --> 00:01:31,570
It will probably just startle them awake.

16
00:01:33,710 --> 00:01:37,790
Will they even remember you were here with all that happening outside?

17
00:01:37,790 --> 00:01:41,490
Even if you die, probably no one would know.

18
00:01:42,460 --> 00:01:43,810
Are you threatening me?

19
00:01:43,810 --> 00:01:46,710
Where are you going to find something of value today?

20
00:01:46,710 --> 00:01:47,750
Wow.

21
00:01:47,750 --> 00:01:51,000
Even though I'm not well off...

22
00:01:56,220 --> 00:01:58,900
- Silver coins?
- If you don't want it,

23
00:02:08,640 --> 00:02:11,110
I-I'll do it.

24
00:02:11,110 --> 00:02:14,360
Even though you seem like a shameful, dirty pervert,

25
00:02:15,430 --> 00:02:18,840
- I will do it.
- Pervert?

26
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:21,350
But only until you fall asleep.

27
00:02:22,180 --> 00:02:24,600
That's all I want.

28
00:02:26,810 --> 00:02:29,500
- You're the one who came here.
- This!

29
00:02:36,290 --> 00:02:37,420
Hey!

30
00:02:37,420 --> 00:02:38,940
What are you doing?

31
00:02:38,940 --> 00:02:43,420
