32
00:02:44,050 --> 00:02:47,820
I see you lack not only manners but also loyalty toward your friend.

33
00:02:47,820 --> 00:02:49,110
What did you say?!

34
00:02:49,110 --> 00:02:52,360
- Don't interfere.
- But still.

35
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:55,240
If you interfere in this fight,

36
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:57,900
you'll only disgrace yourself.

37
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,380
So pathetic.

38
00:03:07,420 --> 00:03:09,770
This insolent Cheonin bastard!

39
00:03:20,030 --> 00:03:23,230
Is there anyone else who wants to come for me?

40
00:03:34,140 --> 00:03:35,570
Let's go.

41
00:03:48,610 --> 00:03:51,190
Do you think you will be let off easily?

42
00:03:51,190 --> 00:03:55,190
The guards will cut your heads off!

43
