44
00:04:05,330 --> 00:04:07,480
they would have been dead by my hands.

45
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:09,180
I know.

46
00:04:09,180 --> 00:04:12,290
You're actually crazy.

47
00:04:12,290 --> 00:04:14,450
I know.

48
00:04:18,870 --> 00:04:20,440
What's wrong?

49
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:23,080
I saw something.

50
00:04:24,790 --> 00:04:26,950
Let's just go for now.

51
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:34,210
You said there is a Cheonin, who saw Sam Maek Jong's face in the capital city.

52
00:04:34,210 --> 00:04:35,490
I apologize.

53
00:04:35,490 --> 00:04:39,480
You can't let him live. Make sure he's dead.

54
00:04:41,820 --> 00:04:45,110
You must find him tonight.

55
00:04:45,110 --> 00:04:47,560
Move quickly. Got it?

56
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:49,790
Yes!

57
00:05:00,230 --> 00:05:04,350
Oh, you're here? You should come in. Why are you just standing there?

58
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:14,720
Why? Didn't you come because of your back?

59
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:18,690
I saw something and it seemed weird.

60
00:05:18,690 --> 00:05:19,950
Did you see something?

61
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:23,180
I feel like I saw that item.

62
00:05:23,180 --> 00:05:24,560
What do you mean by that item?

63
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:27,960
The necklace that the lady wears.

64
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:31,680
The thing that your son had with him.

65
00:05:33,230 --> 00:05:35,520
Where did you see it?

66
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:38,920
In the dark night where the clouds covered the moonlight,

67
00:05:39,980 --> 00:05:45,620
a man was secretly heading to his lover's house,

68
00:05:49,070 --> 00:05:53,180
but he couldn't reveal himself yet.

69
00:05:53,180 --> 00:05:59,510
The man crossed over the fence and snuck into her room like a thief.

70
00:05:59,510 --> 00:06:05,230
The surroundings were dark, but the darkness was comforting.

71
00:06:05,230 --> 00:06:09,330
Passing by countless rooms, at last,

72
00:06:09,330 --> 00:06:12,290
he was able to sense the woman's scent.

73
00:06:12,290 --> 00:06:16,310
As he calmed his heart which was bursting, the moment he opened the door,

74
00:06:16,310 --> 00:06:20,270
In front of his eyes was the woman from his dreams.

75
00:06:20,270 --> 00:06:24,090
She stood there with a bright smile.

76
00:06:24,090 --> 00:06:26,750
Why did you come here?

77
00:06:39,950 --> 00:06:42,170
I lost again.

78
00:07:03,660 --> 00:07:05,920
I'm the scared one.

79
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:15,030
Oh my, Ahn Ji Gong, what are you doing here?

80
00:07:15,030 --> 00:07:18,130
I came because I had something to confirm.

81
00:07:19,050 --> 00:07:20,600
Please tell me what it is.

82
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:25,130
I heard Cheonin villagers came here. Do you know where they went?

83
00:07:25,130 --> 00:07:29,790
Ah, they left about thirty minutes ago.

84
00:07:29,790 --> 00:07:35,010
With the quarrel between Cheonin and the nobles, nobody noticed where they went.

85
00:07:35,010 --> 00:07:39,450
Do you remember what they looked like?

86
00:07:39,450 --> 00:07:44,370
One of them covered his face with a bamboo hat, so I'm not sure about him,

87
00:07:44,370 --> 00:07:48,550
but they were both tall, like you.

88
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:51,730
Thank you.

89
00:07:55,820 --> 00:07:58,190
By chance, do you know this man?

90
00:07:58,190 --> 00:08:00,760
What's happening?

91
00:08:15,390 --> 00:08:18,960
I heard someone who is similar in appearance was headed toward the east gate.

92
00:08:22,940 --> 00:08:26,080
I have something to ask. One of them is wearing a bamboo hat...

93
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:33,460
Let's just stay hidden around here for today and keep looking tomorrow.

94
00:08:33,460 --> 00:08:37,060
When we come to the capital there is not one day when nothing happens.

95
00:08:47,050 --> 00:08:49,260
What's wrong?

96
00:08:50,260 --> 00:08:52,200
It's nothing.

97
00:08:53,180 --> 00:08:56,840
It doesn't seem like nothing.

98
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:59,420
Aren't you going to tell me?

99
00:09:00,230 --> 00:09:01,890
I...

100
00:09:03,490 --> 00:09:07,590
I think I saw the same necklace as mine.

101
00:09:10,610 --> 00:09:14,950
But after coming to the capital, there are so many similar necklaces.

102
00:09:16,620 --> 00:09:20,580
I don't know how many more necklaces there are that look like this.

103
00:09:23,870 --> 00:09:25,600
- Stand up.
- Where are we going?

104
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:30,350
If you even saw some, we'll have to confirm.

105
00:09:30,350 --> 00:09:33,900
Are you stupid? What was the whole point of coming here?

106
00:09:33,900 --> 00:09:36,590
If you saw it, then you should go look.

107
00:09:39,430 --> 00:09:41,870
Aigoo. Stand up.

108
00:09:45,490 --> 00:09:48,430
Why did you come out instead of sleeping?

109
00:09:49,310 --> 00:09:52,630
Because the woman fell asleep on me.

110
00:09:53,750 --> 00:09:56,270
I think I have to see her from time to time.

111
00:09:56,270 --> 00:09:58,160
Do you think she'll do it next time?

112
00:09:58,160 --> 00:10:01,690
Earlier, I definitely heard her call you a pervert...

113
00:10:03,410 --> 00:10:07,900
Don't you think recently we are becoming too close?

114
00:10:07,900 --> 00:10:10,420
I'm starting to think that way.

115
00:10:10,420 --> 00:10:13,870
Even if you don't want to see me, you have no choice for a while.

116
00:10:15,310 --> 00:10:20,120
