124
00:10:58,060 --> 00:11:01,830
Really pretty.

125
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:06,570
You told me differently before. But she seems to be your sister.

126
00:11:06,570 --> 00:11:10,540
No, not just brother and sister. She is the spitting image of me.

127
00:11:10,540 --> 00:11:14,830
She was cute, and she had a small face.

128
00:11:15,490 --> 00:11:17,340
Tall?

129
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,820
What's wrong?

130
00:11:39,630 --> 00:11:41,140
I'm...

131
00:11:42,390 --> 00:11:43,720
I'm done.

132
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:47,850
This is crazy, idiot, you can't! If it happens here, what will I do?

133
00:11:47,850 --> 00:11:51,880
You can't! Get back to your senses!

134
00:11:51,880 --> 00:11:54,570
We have to meet my sister!

135
00:12:13,820 --> 00:12:15,320
We have to hide...

136
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:16,710
What?

137
00:12:16,710 --> 00:12:19,420
Run away...

138
00:12:25,090 --> 00:12:26,750
Shoot!

139
00:12:46,870 --> 00:12:49,550
Dog... Bird!

140
00:13:03,710 --> 00:13:06,990
Dog-Bird. Dog-Bird.

141
00:13:19,940 --> 00:13:21,820
Run away.

142
00:13:21,820 --> 00:13:24,280
Dog-Bird. Dog-Bird.

143
00:14:02,350 --> 00:14:05,090
Stay... Stay still...

144
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:10,010
That's how you'll survive...

145
00:14:45,360 --> 00:14:47,690
At last,

146
00:14:48,700 --> 00:14:50,880
I killed him.

147
00:14:52,460 --> 00:14:55,820
He's still breathing.

148
00:15:48,310 --> 00:15:50,520
Wake up.

149
00:15:50,520 --> 00:15:52,110
Me...

150
00:15:53,400 --> 00:15:57,170
Leave me... And go.

151
00:15:57,170 --> 00:15:59,090
Shut up.

152
00:15:59,620 --> 00:16:01,070
I'll...

153
00:16:03,500 --> 00:16:05,840
I can't...

154
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:10,250
I won't leave you.

155
00:16:10,250 --> 00:16:13,910
I can't lose you. Get up.

156
00:16:21,960 --> 00:16:27,110
You have to live...

157
00:16:28,100 --> 00:16:31,800
You are just myself.

158
00:16:32,410 --> 00:16:34,940
You...

159
00:16:34,940 --> 00:16:37,820
are my parents,

160
00:16:37,820 --> 00:16:40,180
and my sibling,

161
00:16:40,180 --> 00:16:42,770
and my body itself.

162
00:16:43,540 --> 00:16:46,080
If you live, I live.

163
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:48,790
If you die, I die too.

164
00:16:49,830 --> 00:16:51,820
Get up.

165
00:16:51,820 --> 00:16:54,210
Get up, be strong.

166
00:16:54,210 --> 00:16:56,320
Get up...

167
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:58,320
Don't touch that.

168
00:17:58,320 --> 00:17:59,990
This...

169
00:18:02,390 --> 00:18:04,600
Is this yours?

170
00:18:04,600 --> 00:18:06,110
Huh?

171
00:18:11,610 --> 00:18:15,770
Whose necklace is this? It's my child's, right?

172
00:18:16,610 --> 00:18:19,340
Talk to me, please!

173
00:18:31,010 --> 00:18:32,740
Seon Woo...

174
00:18:34,150 --> 00:18:35,790
It's your dad.

175
00:18:38,090 --> 00:18:40,200
Seon Woo!

176
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:42,030
Your dad is here.

177
00:19:17,200 --> 00:19:19,860
Why are you not doing anything?

178
00:19:20,410 --> 00:19:22,180
Save him.

179
00:19:24,090 --> 00:19:26,570
Save him.

180
00:19:37,650 --> 00:19:39,360
Seon Woo.

181
00:20:02,950 --> 00:20:04,330
Dad...

182
00:20:06,490 --> 00:20:10,810
Fa... Father.

183
00:20:12,150 --> 00:20:15,350
I...

184
00:20:18,870 --> 00:20:23,080
I missed you.

185
00:20:23,080 --> 00:20:25,960
I missed you.

186
00:20:59,280 --> 00:21:01,670
Seon Woo.

187
00:21:02,480 --> 00:21:05,210
No way.

188
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:08,650
No, Mak Moon!

189
00:21:09,790 --> 00:21:12,490
No!

190
00:21:12,490 --> 00:21:14,590
No!

191
00:21:14,590 --> 00:21:17,830
No! Mak Moon!

192
00:21:17,830 --> 00:21:20,740
NO!!

193
00:21:21,990 --> 00:21:24,080
NO!!

194
00:21:25,390 --> 00:21:28,470
No.

195
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:33,770
No!

196
00:21:33,770 --> 00:21:36,780
