218
00:23:22,950 --> 00:23:25,190
Don't keep me waiting, tell me quickly.

219
00:23:25,800 --> 00:23:28,310
Actually...

220
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:32,030
There were two men.

221
00:23:32,030 --> 00:23:34,280
Were they handsome?

222
00:23:35,390 --> 00:23:38,150
