228
00:24:02,470 --> 00:24:04,710
That's all I want.

229
00:24:06,740 --> 00:24:10,440
One is mysterious and the other one is deadly.

230
00:24:10,440 --> 00:24:12,750
Do you suppose so?

231
00:24:13,860 --> 00:24:17,770
What happens afterward? Does the woman get involved with the two men?

232
00:24:18,790 --> 00:24:20,580
I suppose?

233
00:24:20,580 --> 00:24:23,720
Will there be a 'next time' ?

234
00:24:24,310 --> 00:24:27,760
What? They should get involved to make it fun.

235
00:24:28,560 --> 00:24:33,210
Queen Dowager, Kakgan Yeong Sil is here.
(Kakgan is the highest officer rank in Silla)

236
00:24:37,720 --> 00:24:41,730
