245
00:25:14,160 --> 00:25:18,980
I mean after killing all the rats lurking around the palace.

246
00:25:40,670 --> 00:25:44,590
Were you waiting for Miss Ah Ro?

247
00:25:44,590 --> 00:25:47,600
No, I wouldn't call it waiting.

248
00:25:47,600 --> 00:25:49,590
No, wait.

249
00:25:49,590 --> 00:25:51,890
- Miss?
- Yes.

250
00:25:52,450 --> 00:25:55,850
She is Ahn Ji Gong's daughter.

251
00:25:55,850 --> 00:26:01,120
Her family isn't doing so well. So, sometimes we give her some sewing to do.

252
00:26:02,650 --> 00:26:07,080
As you know, her talents lie elsewhere.

253
00:26:07,080 --> 00:26:09,490
Ahn Ji Gong?

254
00:26:10,880 --> 00:26:12,720
Does that mean she's a true bone (related to royalty but not the immediate family of the king).

255
00:26:12,720 --> 00:26:15,150
Well...

256
00:26:15,150 --> 00:26:18,600
Let me tell you this.

257
00:26:18,600 --> 00:26:21,250
She is half.

258
00:26:21,250 --> 00:26:22,610
Half?

259
00:26:22,610 --> 00:26:26,280
Her mother was the servant of Ahn Ji Gong's house

260
00:26:26,280 --> 00:26:29,110
and was kicked away to a Cheonin village.

261
00:26:29,110 --> 00:26:32,080
We can say she's half true bone.

262
00:26:42,820 --> 00:26:44,800
You startled me!

263
00:26:46,660 --> 00:26:49,090
I...

264
00:26:49,090 --> 00:26:54,590
Father, about last night...

265
00:26:54,590 --> 00:26:57,050
I...

266
00:26:57,850 --> 00:26:59,430
I...

267
00:27:05,240 --> 00:27:08,360
Did something happen?

268
00:27:10,510 --> 00:27:12,960
Father...

269
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:16,220
There is a serious patient inside.

270
00:27:16,220 --> 00:27:21,350
Because the wound is so deep, rest is needed, so you shouldn't go in there.

271
00:27:22,700 --> 00:27:25,260
Are you okay?

272
00:27:26,710 --> 00:27:29,220
I will not be taking any other patients for a while.

273
00:27:29,220 --> 00:27:33,850
If anyone asks, tell them I went far away to see a patient.

274
00:27:42,100 --> 00:27:44,890
What kind of patient could it be?

275
00:28:27,830 --> 00:28:31,880
You must live. You have to live.

276
00:28:32,480 --> 00:28:35,020
DOCTOR

277
00:30:00,590 --> 00:30:02,290
You've gotten up?

278
00:30:04,350 --> 00:30:05,930
It's okay.

279
00:30:05,930 --> 00:30:08,930
This is...my house.

280
00:30:08,930 --> 00:30:11,600
You've been unconscious for

281
00:30:11,600 --> 00:30:13,780
five days.

282
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:16,700
What about Mak Moon?

283
00:30:18,780 --> 00:30:20,760
Seon Woo...

284
00:30:21,950 --> 00:30:24,330
I buried him well.

285
00:30:27,170 --> 00:30:29,660
You should have saved him.

286
00:30:31,230 --> 00:30:33,990
You said you're a doctor.

287
00:30:33,990 --> 00:30:37,110
You should have saved him.

288
00:30:37,110 --> 00:30:39,850
Why didn't you do anything?

289
00:30:43,340 --> 00:30:47,160
If you hadn't kicked Mak Moon away to the Cheonin village,

290
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:50,430
if you'd stayed with him, he wouldn't have died.

291
00:30:50,430 --> 00:30:54,210
Why didn't you do anything? How could you not save him?

292
00:30:54,210 --> 00:30:56,810
Why did you kill him? Why?

293
00:30:59,170 --> 00:31:01,830
It's not your fault.

294
00:31:05,520 --> 00:31:08,430
How much he missed his family.

295
00:31:09,660 --> 00:31:12,790
He wanted to find them so badly.

296
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:15,950
He did.

297
00:31:16,890 --> 00:31:21,630
I searched and searched for him all over Silla.

298
00:31:23,670 --> 00:31:25,800
It's all because of me.

299
00:31:26,610 --> 00:31:29,590
Even though they took my son, I just watched.

300
00:31:30,850 --> 00:31:33,800
Incapable and powerless.

301
00:31:34,910 --> 00:31:36,730
It's because of his father, me.

302
00:31:58,950 --> 00:32:03,780
How did you live with that condition? You must have fainted often.

303
00:32:05,210 --> 00:32:08,550
It's none of your business whether I die or not.

304
00:32:08,550 --> 00:32:10,810
If I found Seon Woo,

305
00:32:12,330 --> 00:32:16,330
I was going to give him these clothes and the entrance pass to the capital city.

306
00:32:16,330 --> 00:32:23,190
If you plan to go back to the Cheonin village, take these with you. You will pass the gate with ease.

307
00:32:23,190 --> 00:32:25,020
Cheonin.

308
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:29,780
Do Cheonin have to die like beasts?

309
00:32:36,790 --> 00:32:40,410
It is not a crime to kill a Cheonin, who snuck into the capital city.

310
00:32:40,410 --> 00:32:45,810
What is the big deal to climb over the wall into the capital?

311
00:32:46,850 --> 00:32:48,870
Why are we nothing? Why?

312
00:32:48,870 --> 00:32:53,530
That is the disgusting rule of this country, Silla.

313
00:32:54,820 --> 00:32:58,310
- It's not a simple issue.
- What's not simple?

314
00:32:58,310 --> 00:33:02,540
I saw them. I saw who killed Mak Moon.

315
00:33:02,540 --> 00:33:06,740
We can get revenge. We can just get revenge for everything!

316
00:33:56,540 --> 00:33:58,720
Um,

317
00:33:58,720 --> 00:34:02,160
I am the daughter of this household.

318
00:34:02,160 --> 00:34:04,740
I'm Ahn Ji Gong's child.

319
00:34:14,950 --> 00:34:20,620
It's not much. It seemed like you weren't eating at all.

320
00:34:20,620 --> 00:34:26,740
I don't know how bad your body condition is, but it will only get better if you eat.

321
00:34:30,520 --> 00:34:33,280
Did I tell you what my sister looks like?

322
00:34:34,610 --> 00:34:38,300
She has pinky chubby cheeks,

323
00:34:38,300 --> 00:34:42,330
and her eyes are round and sparkling.

324
00:34:42,330 --> 00:34:44,700
She looks just like me!

325
00:34:44,700 --> 00:34:46,930
She was modest and good.

326
00:34:46,930 --> 00:34:50,220
What about a six year old is modest...

327
00:34:51,910 --> 00:34:57,730
I wanted to give her a piggyback ride and watch her get married.

328
00:35:00,270 --> 00:35:04,350
Okay! When I go to the capital,

329
00:35:04,350 --> 00:35:06,530
I'll give you my sister.

330
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:10,080
Why?!

331
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:13,560
- What kind of reaction is that?
- You said she looks like you!

332
00:35:13,560 --> 00:35:14,910
What's wrong with that?!

333
00:35:14,910 --> 00:35:18,930
There are things you should and shouldn't say. He only thinks of himself.

334
00:35:18,930 --> 00:35:21,960
Are you implying that I'm ugly? Huh?

335
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:24,650
Did you just diss me?

336
00:35:26,130 --> 00:35:28,200
Hey!

337
00:35:30,910 --> 00:35:34,680
Let it go. Let it go.

338
00:35:46,510 --> 00:35:50,900
If you drink this, your headache will go away and it will calm down your anger.

339
00:35:50,900 --> 00:35:52,700
It's that type of tea, so . . .

340
00:35:56,640 --> 00:35:59,790
I'll leave it here.

341
00:36:07,300 --> 00:36:09,010
Okay.

342
00:36:09,760 --> 00:36:11,650
You are kind.

343
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:15,770
What did you just say?

344
00:36:21,950 --> 00:36:23,720
I said thank you.

345
00:36:24,320 --> 00:36:28,660
Please drink it. You'll still have to live.

346
00:36:38,930 --> 00:36:42,740
You did well. He'll decide on his own whether he'll drink it or not.

347
00:36:42,740 --> 00:36:45,160
But still,

348
00:36:45,160 --> 00:36:47,760
I hope he will drink it.

349
00:36:49,160 --> 00:36:52,830
What man's appearance from the rear looks so sad?

350
00:37:01,530 --> 00:37:03,220
But still...

351
00:37:04,070 --> 00:37:06,350
I will have to live.

352
00:37:37,340 --> 00:37:39,590
Why are you here?

353
00:37:44,460 --> 00:37:46,790
I asked why you are here?

354
00:37:49,930 --> 00:37:51,760
Just wait.

355
00:37:53,090 --> 00:37:55,750
I will not leave alone

356
00:37:56,420 --> 00:37:58,740
the men who did this to you.

357
00:38:00,530 --> 00:38:02,840
I will get revenge.

358
00:38:12,240 --> 00:38:16,940
The guards were chasing after Cheonin who snuck into the capital.

359
00:38:16,940 --> 00:38:20,480
- Was it also surreptitiously?
- Yes.

360
00:38:20,480 --> 00:38:24,690
Yes. Not even in their uniforms. They moved very quietly.

361
00:38:24,690 --> 00:38:30,450
The guards were supposed to be with the queen dowager. Instead, they were out of uniform searching for a Cheonin?

362
00:38:30,450 --> 00:38:32,530
They must have seen something?

363
00:38:32,530 --> 00:38:34,900
I have seen those men before.

364
00:38:34,900 --> 00:38:37,320
Just give me an order.

365
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:42,750
They must have seen something so important that the queen dowager personally intervened.

366
00:38:43,780 --> 00:38:46,850
This is amusing.

367
00:38:48,770 --> 00:38:52,570
Then go find them. Those Cheonin.

368
00:39:02,210 --> 00:39:06,990
We're not hearing any news from them. Aren't you worried?

369
00:39:06,990 --> 00:39:08,720
Why should I?

370
00:39:09,510 --> 00:39:14,920
They ran away from me. No use worrying about them.

371
00:39:37,320 --> 00:39:39,000
Uncle...

372
00:39:41,380 --> 00:39:43,780
Mak Moon died.

373
00:39:47,190 --> 00:39:50,920
- Because of me.
- It was destiny.

374
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:52,950
Why would it be your fault?

375
00:39:53,970 --> 00:39:58,620
He was asking for death as soon as he climbed the wall.

376
00:39:59,660 --> 00:40:01,080
Uncle.

377
00:40:02,550 --> 00:40:06,000
I need to know why Mak Moon died.

378
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:08,490
And I will definitely get revenge.

379
00:40:08,490 --> 00:40:11,870
It's your fate to just live and stay here.

380
00:40:11,870 --> 00:40:14,970
So just live with me.

381
00:40:14,970 --> 00:40:17,830
You know what kind of person I am.

382
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:42,550
Hurry up and go inside! And don't start crying because I'm not home.

383
00:40:42,550 --> 00:40:45,300
And make sure you eat!

384
00:40:45,930 --> 00:40:50,080
And quit crafting those instruments already. Your back is hurting, too.

385
00:40:53,500 --> 00:40:56,140
If I stay alive,

386
00:40:56,140 --> 00:40:59,290
if I end up staying alive, I promise to come back!

387
00:41:08,940 --> 00:41:12,730
That fate... I can't do anything about it.

388
00:41:19,710 --> 00:41:23,230
Your Majesty, Wi Hwa Gong is here to see you.

389
00:41:23,230 --> 00:41:25,640
The Royal Council will have strong objections.

390
00:41:25,640 --> 00:41:31,070
I wouldn't have started it if I was scared of those objections.

391
00:41:31,070 --> 00:41:32,890
If so, please give me total control over this matter.

392
00:41:32,890 --> 00:41:37,320
I made up my mind when I went to see you in prison.

393
00:41:38,110 --> 00:41:40,510
When do you plan on telling the world?

394
00:41:40,510 --> 00:41:45,280
Since you decided to become the master,

395
00:41:45,280 --> 00:41:48,590
I will announce it to the whole country.

396
00:42:24,450 --> 00:42:28,470
Hwarang

397
00:42:32,150 --> 00:42:35,820
The new intelligentsia for Silla.

398
00:42:35,820 --> 00:42:40,460
Hwarang. Boys who are lovely as flowers.

399
00:42:40,460 --> 00:42:45,630
Regardless of their family or clan, they will lay down their lives for the nation and its people,

400
00:42:45,630 --> 00:42:48,090
Loyal soldiers.

401
00:42:48,090 --> 00:42:52,030
The wisdom to plan the future of Silla,

402
00:42:52,030 --> 00:42:54,450
wise officers.

403
00:42:54,450 --> 00:42:59,400
They will be respected by all of the Silla people.

404
00:42:59,400 --> 00:43:03,240
Beautiful and special beings.

405
00:43:03,240 --> 00:43:08,100
This is me making the future of this kingdom.

406
00:43:09,160 --> 00:43:11,410
It's Hwarang.

407
00:43:12,470 --> 00:43:17,680
Yes. This kingdom will become stronger with Hwarang.

408
00:43:34,910 --> 00:43:38,600
Among the noblemen, only beautiful ones will be selected.

409
00:43:38,600 --> 00:43:40,990
They will study hard together

410
00:43:40,990 --> 00:43:47,190
and enjoy the beauty of nature in order to become the intelligentsia of Silla's future

411
00:43:47,990 --> 00:43:50,260
Hwarang.

412
00:43:50,260 --> 00:43:53,280
Wow. That sounds cool!

413
00:43:54,610 --> 00:43:57,930
They are pulling out dogs for the queen dowager.

414
00:43:59,030 --> 00:44:01,010
- Is that not it?
- I know right.

415
00:44:01,010 --> 00:44:04,670
Who is going to do such crap? Isn't that so, Ban Ryu?

416
00:44:04,670 --> 00:44:07,830
I didn't know you would be interested in this.

417
00:44:08,820 --> 00:44:10,980
Why? You want to do it?

418
00:44:10,980 --> 00:44:14,690
Why don't you go and wag your tail?
(figure of speech: sucking up)

419
00:44:16,520 --> 00:44:19,340
Isn't tail wagging your specialty?

420
00:44:19,960 --> 00:44:23,030
It's what you always do to your godfather.

421
00:44:26,800 --> 00:44:30,830
We are speaking so elegantly.

422
00:44:30,830 --> 00:44:32,950
Is that right?

423
00:44:33,600 --> 00:44:35,510
Do you want to compete?

424
00:44:40,180 --> 00:44:44,680
The whole capital is shaking up due to the notice from the queen dowager.

425
00:44:44,680 --> 00:44:46,550
Are you still going to do nothing?

426
00:44:46,550 --> 00:44:49,250
That is obviously a hostage, isn't it?

427
00:44:49,250 --> 00:44:53,620
Taking our kids and making them to be guards for her.

428
00:44:53,620 --> 00:44:56,990
She will keep all her power right under her feet.

429
00:44:56,990 --> 00:45:00,250
Collect the noble kids and train them

430
00:45:00,250 --> 00:45:04,180
to be future intelligentsia.

431
00:45:04,180 --> 00:45:06,510
Why are you guys so upset?

432
00:45:06,510 --> 00:45:08,700
What did you say?

433
00:45:08,700 --> 00:45:11,820
Why don't you say something, Yeong Sil Gong?

434
00:45:11,820 --> 00:45:15,050
Why aren't you saying anything?

435
00:45:15,050 --> 00:45:19,670
They'll be training a group for the future of our kingdom.

436
00:45:19,670 --> 00:45:23,890
There's no reason to not send our sons.

437
00:45:24,490 --> 00:45:25,620
What?

438
00:45:25,620 --> 00:45:27,140
Wait.

439
00:45:28,660 --> 00:45:32,950
We can't just send them.

440
00:45:32,950 --> 00:45:36,490
I have to get an approval from King Jin Heung?

441
00:45:36,490 --> 00:45:42,410
Yes. That's it. You must show us if you are trustworthy.

442
00:45:42,410 --> 00:45:43,560
Trustworthy?

443
00:45:43,560 --> 00:45:46,500
The future of Silla belongs to King Jin Heung.

444
00:45:46,500 --> 00:45:50,860
This kind of big future plan requires the king's approval.

445
00:45:50,860 --> 00:45:54,690
If you do, the Royal Council will send their kids with their assurance.

446
00:45:54,690 --> 00:45:57,640
Cunning old man.

447
00:45:57,640 --> 00:46:00,660
He is trying to get Sam Maek Jong out of hiding.

448
00:46:00,660 --> 00:46:03,430
Please consider

449
00:46:03,430 --> 00:46:07,640
our concerns as parents before being officers for Silla.

450
00:46:10,260 --> 00:46:14,400
The intelligentsia for the future of the country... Beautiful appearance?

451
00:46:14,400 --> 00:46:17,500
- That's ME!
- Enjoy the beauty of nature? That's me!

452
00:46:18,130 --> 00:46:21,490
For the future of Silla, Hwarang.

453
00:46:24,500 --> 00:46:27,730
You mean Hwarang for yourself, Mother.

454
00:46:33,230 --> 00:46:36,760
For now, take seven silver coins.

455
00:46:38,100 --> 00:46:42,240
What's up? Paying off the debt?

456
00:46:46,850 --> 00:46:50,360
How much was left?

457
00:46:51,450 --> 00:46:55,580
I had some work for you...

458
00:46:55,580 --> 00:46:57,730
That's not it.

459
00:46:58,930 --> 00:47:02,390
What is it? I asked you what it is.

460
00:47:04,090 --> 00:47:06,830
Aren't you going to tell me?

461
00:47:08,950 --> 00:47:14,440
This was asked in such a  secret way...

462
00:47:14,440 --> 00:47:18,380
It requires observing and prompt abilities.

463
00:47:18,380 --> 00:47:23,130
You need to hide well and run away quickly.

464
00:47:24,030 --> 00:47:29,390
That is my specialty.

465
00:47:29,390 --> 00:47:31,800
What can I do?

466
00:47:35,330 --> 00:47:36,520
So,

467
00:47:36,520 --> 00:47:39,650
is the favor I asked of you going well?

468
00:47:40,400 --> 00:47:44,190
Suspicions, really.

469
00:47:44,190 --> 00:47:47,960
Don't worry! I did as you said,

470
00:47:47,960 --> 00:47:50,390
and I got someone.

471
00:47:50,390 --> 00:47:52,800
Just one?

472
00:47:52,800 --> 00:47:57,350
You have a smaller sized mind than I expected. I thought it was a bowl, but

473
00:47:57,350 --> 00:48:00,420
it was a sauce dish.

474
00:48:00,420 --> 00:48:05,320
Isn't it important to do this in a secretive and casual way?

475
00:48:05,320 --> 00:48:08,490
Because if the word should get out in the neigborhood, because it's unusual,

476
00:48:08,490 --> 00:48:12,500
would you want that? Just look after your part timer well

477
00:48:12,500 --> 00:48:17,100
I left it to the best person.

478
00:48:17,100 --> 00:48:19,130
Geez.

479
00:48:20,460 --> 00:48:24,770
Why is he acting like that? Who did he get?

480
00:48:24,770 --> 00:48:28,200
Who on earth did he hire to be that confident?

481
00:49:29,100 --> 00:49:32,230
No.

482
00:49:33,120 --> 00:49:36,450
It's not right. It's not right.

483
00:49:48,030 --> 00:49:50,320
By chance...

484
00:49:50,320 --> 00:49:54,770
Are you the bamboo hat with the necklace? Am I right?

485
00:49:56,750 --> 00:50:00,950
Anyway, I told Ahn Ji Gong about you.

486
00:50:00,950 --> 00:50:05,120
Did your friend meet his father?

487
00:50:05,120 --> 00:50:07,930
It was all thanks to me.

488
00:50:07,930 --> 00:50:11,700
I am not trying to show off.

489
00:50:15,080 --> 00:50:17,050
Is that not it?

490
00:50:17,050 --> 00:50:19,590
Or not.

491
00:50:21,360 --> 00:50:23,830
I need a good sword.

492
00:50:23,830 --> 00:50:25,640
Sword?

493
00:50:26,550 --> 00:50:29,220
Hmm. I had looked around briefly.

494
00:50:29,220 --> 00:50:32,780
Where could a noble man go?

495
00:50:34,110 --> 00:50:36,010
Okta store?

496
00:50:39,670 --> 00:50:41,500
Because I like you.

497
00:50:41,500 --> 00:50:44,820
Leave it out!

498
00:50:47,080 --> 00:50:49,780
Okay, here.

499
00:50:52,920 --> 00:50:56,390
In order to find a guy who likes arrows, I need to go to a carpenter's shop.

500
00:50:56,390 --> 00:50:58,660
Good.

501
00:51:07,250 --> 00:51:09,770
It's my first time following someone like that.

502
00:51:09,770 --> 00:51:14,490
For all day, how fast she runs around.

503
00:51:14,490 --> 00:51:17,410
So, where is she now?

504
00:51:48,600 --> 00:51:52,460
Finally, I killed this man.

505
00:51:52,460 --> 00:51:54,470
It is that bastard.

506
00:52:18,490 --> 00:52:21,760
It must be difficult to get around like that.

507
00:53:56,680 --> 00:53:58,720
Excuse me...

508
00:54:08,550 --> 00:54:10,820
Excuse me...

509
00:54:28,540 --> 00:54:30,360
Mother!

510
00:54:32,460 --> 00:54:34,790
I have no intention to hurt you.

511
00:54:34,790 --> 00:54:38,670
If you make a noise, you may be killed by the assassin following me.

512
00:55:02,220 --> 00:55:03,810
Come out!

513
00:55:05,320 --> 00:55:07,790
Who is following me?

514
00:55:10,130 --> 00:55:12,600
Is hiding one of your habits?

515
00:55:13,360 --> 00:55:15,760
Are you that afraid of your face being seen?

516
00:55:23,280 --> 00:55:26,510
Go and don't look back and I'll see you again another time.

517
00:55:41,930 --> 00:55:44,650
Where exactly is the door?

518
00:55:50,110 --> 00:55:52,610
I asked who you were.

519
00:55:54,290 --> 00:55:56,380
To you...

520
00:55:58,520 --> 00:56:00,470
I'm someone who is owed a debt from you.

521
00:56:00,470 --> 00:56:05,670
Well. I cannot remember owing a debt to anyone.

522
00:56:07,310 --> 00:56:10,820
My friend was killed by the sword you brandished.

523
00:56:11,420 --> 00:56:13,770
Does this help you remember?

524
00:56:16,300 --> 00:56:17,990
Stop.

525
00:56:20,800 --> 00:56:22,870
Finally, I

526
00:56:24,040 --> 00:56:26,930
killed this man.

527
00:56:26,930 --> 00:56:31,210
He is still breathing.

528
00:56:31,210 --> 00:56:35,330
- He was alive.
- Stop hiding and come out you cowardly bastard!

529
00:56:35,330 --> 00:56:37,990
Come out right now!

530
00:57:20,670 --> 00:57:24,690
There are doors in this world that people like you should not dare to open.

531
00:57:24,690 --> 00:57:27,290
It seems like you are in front of that door right now.

532
00:57:27,290 --> 00:57:30,380
Do you think it's alright to have roads

533
00:57:30,380 --> 00:57:35,380
that people can't cross, doors you can't open?

534
00:57:35,380 --> 00:57:40,160
Do you think that is alright?

535
00:57:41,680 --> 00:57:46,550
I do not. I think it's all rubbish.

536
00:57:46,550 --> 00:57:49,020
So, stop barking and come out!

537
00:57:51,510 --> 00:57:54,290
